///|
/// Decoder convention for converting a Row into a typed struct.
/// Generated types define a `decode` static method that takes Row and returns Self.
/// This is a naming convention, not a trait — MoonBit 0.1 doesn't support
/// trait objects or generic trait methods needed for a formal Decoder interface.
